name: GreenGrapes
description:
This local fruit market is held on Thursdays each week, it's called Thursday bāzār. My grandmother shops her grocery needs here every week. She drives a car in the road for 5 minutes, near a river until she arrives at the city. She then exits the first square to the right. The Bazaar begins near 10 and will go on until the sunset.
